GoWitness
---------
from: Heath Adams - The Cyber Mentor ; Practical Ethical Hacking - The Complete Course
"Screenshotting Websites with GoWitness" - https://academy.tcm-sec.com/courses/1152300/lectures/24781576

GoWitness - https://github.com/sensepost/gowitness

Installation:

$ go get -u gorm.io/gorm
# installs a dependency that is currently broken when HA recorded the lecture

From installation page: "Use go install github.com/sensepost/gowitness@latest if you have the go binary in your $PATH"
$ go install github.com/sensepost/gowitness@latest
